</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Preventive maintenance</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-9848D934-FF3E-4AC9-BA07-69028FA44036" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-7F50F10D-99BF-4A90-8BCE-B81E84A4F98C" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Methyl Benzoate</title><p class="- topic/p ">Application : Intended for use on the <ph varid="productname" class="- topic/ph ">Colorado M-Series</ph> for cleaning matrix plate, wipers and/or clean wall. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Contents : Methyl Benzoate 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Cleaning takes place at 70°C . 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Methyl benzoate will be used in its pure form (100 w% liquid). 
</p></section><section id="GUID-591E4806-2742-45D0-963E-2906273BC9C0" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Cleaner K</title><p class="- topic/p ">Application: General purpose cleaning. Used for removing cured ink for example on the platen. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Content: IPA, Isopropyl alcohol 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Disadvantage: Flammable, harmful. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">To order see : 
<xref keyref="25SERVTOOLS001" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-E38A6882-2820-4865-A496-9DDE279FA971.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 25 Service tools?>25 Service tools</xref> 
</p></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-AE482382-4925-4EFB-985E-8DF8BE795C1D.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Preventive maintenance</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
